        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-12-22T21:15:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "When I suggested that we needed a mutex, I was expecting to see a pthread_mutex, but this is so much nicer. I welcome the new modern C++ world!",
      "revId": "8a7b65dc9e8973119c2ed6db733f8695d195d5f9",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
